/-- **Clear loop body ‚Äî delete branch (Risk C2, step 3).** When register `dst` is
nonempty, the loop body `clearBodyRawTM dst` navigates to it, tests its content
start (nonzero ‚Üí content branch), deletes the first cell and rewinds, landing at
`clearBodyRawTM_exitLoop dst` with the tape `encodeTape (s.set dst (s.get
